Sentencas: The level of barium doping in lanthanum strontium titanate (La0.4Sr0.6-xBaxTiO3, 0 <= x <= 0.2; LST, x = 0; LSBT, x > 0), prepared by solid state synthesis, affects its performance as anode in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Effect of Ba doping on performance of LST as anode in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Cell structures of LST and all LSBT were similar.
Titulo: Effect of Ba doping on performance of LST as anode in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The oxidation state of Ti in all compounds was reduced by a comparable amount when LST or LSBT was heated under reducing conditions to form La0.4Sr0.6-xBaxTi0.594+Ti0.413+O2.97.
Titulo: Effect of Ba doping on performance of LST as anode in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: All fuel cells using LST or LSBT had high activity for conversion of hydrogen or methane, and the activity increased with the level of substitution by Ba.
Titulo: Effect of Ba doping on performance of LST as anode in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In addition, performance was enhanced when H2S Was present in either CH4 or H-2 fuel.
Titulo: Effect of Ba doping on performance of LST as anode in solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: There was good contact between YSZ electrolyte and each LSBT or LSB anode.
Titulo: Effect of Ba doping on performance of LST as anode in solid oxide fuel cells
